{"tid":917227,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"來看什麼地區的行動網路比 WiFi 快","createTime":"2018-11-26T09:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T14:17:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f55fd91e010e5bcaeb44c651f3008016a6a571a2","tid":917227,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-US%2Fhomerun%2Fengadget_479%2Fb2fbd9f93be4ff6e0f426c0f49b1bedb&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=111e76e9e05c2b7fc9fe17fc8e970a00feae3fae\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fmedia.zenfs.com%252Fen-US%252Fhomerun%252Fengadget_479%252Fb2fbd9f93be4ff6e0f426c0f49b1bedb%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D111e76e9e05c2b7fc9fe17fc8e970a00feae3fae&h=f61c6dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果可以的話，大概 WiFi 會是大家電話連網的首選方式，其中一個原因是它在速度上比行動網路優勝。然而，這想法原來在不少地方都不適用啊。OpenSignal 最近發表了一份有趣的研究，表示有 33 個國家和地區的平均行動網路速度還要比 WiFi 更快，而且差距也不少啊。<br />\n<br />\n據報告所說，行動網路比 WiFi 明顯快最多的地區是澳洲，差距達 13Mbps，當地平均行動網路下載速度達 34.6Mbps，但 WiFi 只有 21.6Mbps；第二名是黎巴嫩，當地的行動網路下載速度雖然僅有 14.8Mbps，但 WiFi 平均速度卻更只有 2.5Mbps；法國的差距也有 2.5Mbps，行動網路的平均下載速度有 20.2Mbps，WiFi 只有 17.7Mbps。榜上大多都是中東、歐洲、拉丁美洲的地區，但想不到台灣也榜上有名，行動網路平均下載速度比 WiFi 快 1.6Mpbs，不過兩個網路下載速度分別都有 27.8Mbps 和 26.3Mbps，但也不算是會影響使用體驗的了。<br />\n<br />\n報告中也有提供 WiFi 速度比行動網路更快的比較數字，才發現香港的 WiFi 速度平均能達 53.3Mbps，但行動網路卻只有 14.7Mbps... 難怪香港那麼多人會黏住有免費 WiFi 提供的地方了。中國大陸的 WiFi 下載速度平均也有 23.9Mbps，比平均 13.8Mbps 的行動網路快一些。新加坡、美國等先進地區也同樣仍是 WiFi 比行動網路快。<br />\n<br />\nOpenSignal 表示，這報告說明了行動網路的發展已經非常成熟，尤其是 4G 技術的出現，扭轉了過往利用固網資源的 WiFi 比較快的印象，所以未來 WiFi 和行動網路的關係定會改變，尤其在速度更快的商用 5G 連網開始普及之後。自然，智慧型電話裡的 WiFi 助手功能似乎也會被淘汰了吧，畢竟轉用 WiFi 也不一定代表有更好的使用體驗了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?crop=1600%2C960%2C0%2C0&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;resize=1600%2C960&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-11%2Fbd2edef0-f0e6-11e8-9ff1-aa40e9059eda&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=b46e86752feeea5ef8dc271c12d5ed851db4eec9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fcrop%3D1600%252C960%252C0%252C0%26quality%3D85%26format%3Djpg%26resize%3D1600%252C960%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2018-11%252Fbd2edef0-f0e6-11e8-9ff1-aa40e9059eda%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3Db46e86752feeea5ef8dc271c12d5ed851db4eec9&h=55960374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/26/mobile-internet-faster-than-wifi-in-33-countries/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2Fmobile-internet-faster-than-wifi-in-33-countries%2F&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=47e20ac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/26/mobile-internet-faster-than-wifi-in-33-countries/</a>"},{"pid":"25302032e1294a4730864c2fc37a0d49979d7551","tid":917227,"uid":118647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"香港4g速度比啲限速Plan拖低哂個平均數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cc6f7246f0cd8d7bd6738188582e4beef44eaa","tid":917227,"uid":20890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"想知韓國同日本 新加坡呢三個"},{"pid":"c7a25bd9487ab92522a11db2d83443c7df794079","tid":917227,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25302032e1294a4730864c2fc37a0d49979d7551","tid":917227,"uid":118647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"香港4g速度比啲限速Plan拖低哂個平均數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:10:33.000Z","msg":"平均數對用家黎講冇好處,<br />\n香港平均高又唔代表你網速一定快<br />\n人地限速所以先可以俾有錢人高速wo"},{"pid"